songs.title: Wolverine
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from snippet

[Intro]
Wolverine
Wolverine, wolverine, wolverine

[Chorus]
Wolverine, wolverine, wolverine
Wolverine, wolverine, wolverine, wolverine
Oh, wolverine, yeah
Wolverine, wolverine, wolverine
Wolverine, wolverine, wolverine, wolverine

[Verse 1]
Get green, you can swallow my kids, drink the Similac
I'm on the back like Latricia [?]
Fuck around me, bitch, I keep the MAC
Got some paper, call me office mats
Knife to his throat, take his Adam's apple
Put it in the bottle, Snapple apple
Beat you, word on the block like we playin' Scrabble
I keep dicks on the Glock but I never jam 'em
I snap on the beat like the Laffy Taffy
Squigged up, I need a Krabby Patty
I'm stealin' food, pockets full of salad
These niggas my kids, make they meals happy
I might go cray just to feel happy
Big .30 and she still grab it
Put the knife on his face like a fucking savage
I smoke his crew like a fuckin' faggot
Bitch, I got tricks like Inspector Gadget
...

I got them stars on my roof (Hey)
Patrick ceilin' in the coupe (Gang, gang)
Bitch, I'm a dog, I say, "Roof" (Yeah, yeah)
I'm at your neck like a noose
Bitch, I'm a monkey like Boots
